<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنَا الْمَرْوَزِيُّ قَالَ:</span> سُئِلَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ عَنْ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">حَدِيثِ النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">((ضَرَبْتُ بِيَدِي فَإِذَا مِسْكٌ أَذْفَرُ)</span>) .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> الَّذِي لَا خَلْطَ لَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>